div.div: The luck that didn't appear in my whole life, appeared right before I quit the game! Lee Ki-Ho, who was about to turn his life around, got a rare item that none of the 400 million players could get in the world's first virtual reality game ! "Isn't this a real life changer?" (Source: KakaoPage, translated)

Hamel is a warrior who traveled with his colleagues to exterminate the devil. Unfortunately, he died just before the battle with the devil started.
But then he was reborn as a descendant of his fellow warrior, Vermouth. The very descendant from the bloodline of the great Vermouth, Hamel.
No, he is now Eugene Lionhart. From a dying body to a new body, he has a strength that he did not have in his previous life. Facing a new world where everything is questionable, the journey of his unfinished previous life begins now. (Source: KakaoPage, translated)
